This document describes the structure and architecture at the most basic level.

Database:
  Models:
    User:
      -id
      -username
      -password
    Progress:
      -user-id
      -completed-todo-count
      -completed-daily-count
      -experience
    Activity:
      -id
      -user-id
      -task-description
      -difficulty-level*
    Todos:
      -activity-id
      -end-date (optional)
    Dailies:
      -activity-id